title: Was Capitol Rioter in Horns and Furs an Antifa Instigator Who Took Part in BLM Protests?
subtitle: Conspiracy theorists jumped into action when the unmistakable figure of Trump supporter and QAnon proponent Jake Angeli appeared at the U.S. Capitol riot.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: A photograph showed U.S. Capitol rioter Jake Angeli taking part in a Black Lives Matter march, thus proving he was an instigator and not a Trump supporter.
